To Print All Available Records:
className.all

=> Blog.all


to find specific field:

Article.find(1)    //with id 1
Article.first
Artilce.last


You can also store values in variables:


my_record = article.find(1)

now we can access the fields of my_record.title and my_record.description as there are getters and setters by defaults. 

We can also modify the values:

my_record.title = "New Title"
my_record.save  


NOTE: MAKE SURE YoU SAVE IT AFTER EVERY ROUOND OF CHANGES



